152
00:15:19,833 --> 00:15:21,541
Khoảng 5cm.

153
00:15:23,041 --> 00:15:24,666
Thật nực cười.

154
00:15:27,916 --> 00:15:29,250
Tôi sẽ tạm giữ anh.

155
00:15:31,458 --> 00:15:33,958
Vì nghi mạo danh.

156
00:15:36,875 --> 00:15:37,750
Anh không thể.

157
00:15:54,333 --> 00:15:55,166
Hannah?

158
00:15:56,416 --> 00:15:57,250
Hannah?

159
00:16:00,875 --> 00:16:02,000
Có ai ở nhà không?

160
00:16:06,000 --> 00:16:06,875
Xin chào?

161
00:16:16,916 --> 00:16:17,791
Xin chào?

162
00:16:20,583 --> 00:16:23,125
